    "description": "Dive into a wondrous Match-3 undersea world and let the cares of life drift away! Make matches across sprawling coral reef levels, and collect sparkling treasures to restore magnificent maritime mansions to their erstwhile splendor. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlunge into a spellbinding deep-sea world. Solve mind-bending puzzle challenges with spot the difference scenes and jigsaw puzzles to gather resources. Visit the shop and equip yourself with helpful power-ups as you delve into the fascinating ocean. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDiscover tons of new game play elements like submarines, walls, conveyor belts, octopuses, and more! Savor a delightful, relaxing soundtrack while you explore the vast match-3 levels! Your undersea adventure awaits in Jewel Match Aquascapes!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures<br />\r\n- Explore 220 huge levels!<br />\r\n- 72 additional bonus levels with new game features!<br />\r\n- 3 different play modes: timed, relaxed, and limited moves!<br />\r\n- 3 difficulty settings: normal, advanced and insane.<br />\r\n- Buy dozens of upgrades and power-ups from the shop.<br />\r\n- Replayable mini-games, including jigsaw puzzles and spot the difference scenes.<br />\r\n- Stunning wallpapers.<br />\r\n- Ethereal soundtrack.",
